  step 66: missing (oracle: "\"It's the truth, Harris. If I'm going to jail, so be it, but I won't hang at Traitor's Gate. Hooper was the one who told the boy about our work. Hooper put the boy on to me. I should have realised, of course. These things don't happen by chance. I was a fool to think they might. And then, once he had me compromised, he demanded I steal the part from the machine.\"\n")
